high_descs: turn left, walk to the kitchen island
grab the pan on the island
put the pan in the sink, fill the pan with water
put the pan on the island
anns.task_desc: fill the pan with water, put the pan on the kitchen island

high_descs: Move to the island to the right of you
Pick up a pot from the island
Move to the sink behind you
clean the pot in the sink and fill with water
Move to the island behind you
Put the pot on the island.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with water on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Go to the left and face the counter to the right.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn around and face the sink.
Put the pot in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the pot up.
Turn around and face the counter behind again.
Put the pot down on the right side of the green counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on the counter.
